This app is terrible. If you are looking for an accurate scouting app do not download this! I downloaded it to help identify diseases in corn and soybean fields yet the algorithm has not been able to give any results at all! The weed ID is terrible, I used it on some simple weeds that were isolated in fields and the app got them wrong every time. It identified prickly sida as redroot pigweed and waterhemp as common purslane.
